title: Hepta Stratum: Time Sync
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/time/hopf
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the Stratum for time synchronization of the device.

 This check supports Hepta 8029 and Hepta 8030 devices.

 The check will raise {CRITICAL} if the reported state is "Invalid Stratum", {WARNING} if
 the reported state is "Stratum is using secondary reference (via NTP).

discovery:
 One service is created.

item:
 The fixed statement {{ntpSysStratum}}
